<h1 class="h1">Privacy Policy</h1>

<article class="card section">
  <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> 2026-02-08</p>

  <hr>

  <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
  <p>
    This Privacy Policy explains how Wolium Bot ("Bot", "Service") collects, uses, stores, and protects user data when
    users interact with the Bot through Discord or connected services.
  </p>
  <p>By using the Bot, you agree to this Privacy Policy.</p>

  <hr>

  <h2>2. Data Controller</h2>
  <p><strong>Data Controller:</strong> Arturwolium (Independent Developer)</p>
  <p><strong>Location:</strong> Lithuania, European Union</p>
  <p>
    <strong>Contact:</strong>
    <a href="https://discord.gg/MXupeAApza" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Discord Support Server</a>
  </p>

  <hr>

  <h2>3. Data We Collect</h2>

  <h3>3.1 Discord Data</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>User ID</li>
    <li>Guild / Server ID</li>
    <li>Channel ID</li>
    <li>Command usage data</li>
    <li>Error logs</li>
    <li>Message metadata (timestamps, message links, server/channel/user IDs)</li>
    <li>Voice activity metadata (join time, previous/current channel, server ID, user ID)</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>3.2 Message Content</h3>
  <p>Full message content is stored <strong>only if explicitly enabled or requested by the user</strong>.</p>

  <h3>3.3 Attachments</h3>
  <p>Only attachment links stored by Discord may be stored. The Bot does not store actual uploaded files.</p>

  <h3>3.4 OAuth Data</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Discord OAuth authentication data</li>
    <li>Server list accessible to the user</li>
    <li>Access tokens</li>
    <li>Refresh tokens</li>
  </ul>

  <hr>

  <h2>4. How We Use Data</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Provide bot functionality</li>
    <li>Process commands</li>
    <li>Improve stability and performance</li>
    <li>Provide AI-based features</li>
    <li>Prevent abuse and ensure security</li>
  </ul>

  <hr>

  <h2>5. AI Processing (Third-Party Processing)</h2>
  <p>Some features use third-party AI services via HuggingFace API.</p>

  <p>Data that may be sent to AI processing includes:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Message content (only if enabled by user)</li>
    <li>Server / channel / username</li>
    <li>Permissions data</li>
    <li>Message timestamps</li>
    <li>Reply context</li>
  </ul>

  <p>AI providers may temporarily process data only to generate responses.</p>

  <hr>

  <h2>6. Data Storage</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Database Provider: Supabase</li>
    <li>Region: European Union (eu-central-1)</li>
    <li>Data transmission: Encrypted via HTTPS</li>
    <li>Sensitive tokens: Encrypted at rest</li>
  </ul>

  <hr>

  <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
  <p>Data is stored until:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>User requests deletion, OR</li>
    <li>Data is no longer required for service operation</li>
  </ul>

  <hr>

  <h2>8. Data Deletion</h2>
  <p>Users can request deletion of all stored data using a bot command.</p>
  <p>Currently, deletion removes all stored logs, message history, and voice activity records related to the user.</p>

  <hr>

  <h2>9. Internal Logging</h2>
  <p>Some logs may be stored in private internal Discord channels for debugging and moderation purposes.</p>
  <p>Access is limited to bot administrators and staff only.</p>

  <hr>

  <h2>10. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Discord (Platform Provider)</li>
    <li>Supabase (Database Infrastructure)</li>
    <li>HuggingFace (AI Processing API)</li>
  </ul>

  <hr>

  <h2>11. Security Measures</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Encrypted communication (HTTPS)</li>
    <li>Encrypted storage of sensitive tokens</li>
    <li>Restricted database access</li>
    <li>Access limited to authorized bot staff</li>
  </ul>

  <hr>

  <h2>12. User Rights (GDPR)</h2>
  <p>Users located in the European Union may have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Request access to stored data</li>
    <li>Request deletion of data</li>
    <li>Object to certain processing</li>
    <li>Request correction of incorrect data</li>
  </ul>

  <hr>

  <h2>13. Children</h2>
  <p>
    The Service is not specifically directed toward children. If a parent or guardian believes data was collected from a
    minor, they may contact the Data Controller.
  </p>

  <hr>

  <h2>14. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>
    The Privacy Policy may be updated periodically. Significant changes may be communicated via the Bot or support
    server.
  </p>

